BC Simple Literal HTML Settings README

What is the BC Simple Literal HTML Settings extension?
================================

BC Simple Literal HTML Settings is a true
eZ Publish extension that provides example
settings for global, default ezwebin siteaccesses
to enable the literal html tag. This allows
the user to insert html tags.


BC Simple Literal HTML Settings version
=======================

The current version of BC Simple Literal HTML Settings is 0.3.0
Last Major update: March 25, 2012

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.3.0


